CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 30, 1954, pg. 12, reads: "Ivy Leaf Members - These pretty co-eds who attend school at the University of Pittsburgh recently entered the Ivy Leaf Club of Iota Chapter, Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority. They are clockwise: Stephanie Jonson [Johnson?], Myrna Davis, Lee Brun [LeeBrun] Johnson, Monretta Davis, Barbara Peace and Jo Ann Snyder. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh students from Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, including Stephanie Johnson, Myrna Davis, LeeBrun Johnson, Monretta Davis, Barbara Peace, and Jo Ann Snyder, gathered in living room with small ivy plant, religious picture, and tiled fireplace
